ry/links/hughfoxbio.html\">Profile for Hugh Fox</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i>Dictionary of Midwestern Literature: The authors</i>by Philip A. Greasley, Society for the Study of Midwestern Literature (U.S.) 2001, p. 202,</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-7\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Curt Johnson, December Press, editor-publisher of <i>Who's Who in U.S. Writers, Editors and Poets</i>.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-8\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-8\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Aardwolfe Books, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external free\" href=\"http://www.aardwolfe.com\">http://www.aardwolfe.com</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-9\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-9\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20160304100226/http://www.skylightpress.co.uk/9781908011077.html\">\"Depths and Dragons\"</a>. Archived from <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.skylightpress.co.uk/9781908011077.html\">the original</a> on 2016-03-04.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=Depths+and+Dragons&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.skylightpress.co.uk%2F9781908011077.html&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AHugh+Fox\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-10\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-10\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20160304070536/http://www.skylightpress.co.uk/9781908011091.html\">\"Immortal Jaguar\"</a>. 2016-03-04. Archived from <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.skylightpress.co.uk/9781908011091.html\">the original</a> on 2016-03-04.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=Immortal+Jaguar&amp;rft.date=2016-03-04&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.skylightpress.co.uk%2F9781908011091.html&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AHugh+Fox\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-11\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-11\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external free\" href=\"http://www.skylightpress.co.uk/9781908011398.html\">http://www.skylightpress.co.uk/9781908011398.html</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-12\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-12\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external free\" href=\"http://www.skylightpress.co.uk/fiction.html\">http://www.skylightpress.co.uk/fiction.html</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-13\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-13\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external free\" href=\"http://www.sunburypressstore.com/Who-Me-9781934597514.htm\">http://www.sunburypressstore.com/Who-Me-9781934597514.htm</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-14\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-14\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external free\" href=\"http://www.sunburypressstore.com/Through-a-Glass-Darkly-9781934597453.htm\">http://www.sunburypressstore.com/Through-a-Glass-Darkly-9781934597453.htm</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-15\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-15\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\